text: Contacto Vecinal TV is a Venezuelan community television channel. It was created in February 2005 and can be seen in the community of Suata in the José Féliz Ribas Municipality of the Aragua State of Venezuela on UHF channel 59. Tallulat Henriquez is the legal representative of the foundation that owns this channel.
